Clerics who take the Suffering domain seek to bring pain and torture to the masses, and are granted spells that reflect their cruel nature.

<b>Domain Special Ability and Bonus Spells</b>
- Pain Touch: The cleric is has the ability to infuse the essence of pain into a single touch once per day.  With a melee touch attack, the cleric deals 2 strength and dexterity damage to the target (4 on a critical).

- The cleric gains access to the following spells at the specified spell level: <i>Enervation (4), Feeblemind (5), Destruction (6), Horrid Wilting(9)</i>.